rows.label: tlk400803_msg0001
rows.name:
I did see a boy head over towards the
farm...was he the one you're after?

rows.label: tlk400803_msg0002
rows.name:
I feel like this city's getting less safe
recently... There was that nasty incident
not long ago too, and the water outage.

rows.label: tlk400803_msg0003
rows.name:
Torigo has the biggest Superbian base
in the whole of Gula, you know.

rows.label: tlk400803_msg0004
rows.name:
In other regions, the Superbians don't
have quite as much influence.
I just worry about the future, is all...
